Package DatabaseLayer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataDeleter
    Interface Name: DataDeleter Description: This interface defines the methods which are employed by the DatabaseDeleter class.
    DataReader
    Interface Name: DataReader Description: This interface defines the methods which are employed by the DatabaseReader class.
    DataWriter
    Interface Name: DataWriter Description: This interface defines the methods which are employed by the DatabaseWriter class.
    DeleterDAO
    Interface Name: DeleterDAO Description: This interface provides the data access object used to implement the DataDeleter methods used to access the SQL database.
    ReaderDAO
    Interface Name: ReaderDAO Description: This interface provides the data access object used to implement the DataReader methods used to access the SQL database.
    RFIDDAO  
    RFIDReader  
    WriterDAO
    Interface Name: WriterDAO Description: This interface provides the data access object used to implement the DataWriter methods used to access the SQL database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAOFactory
    Class Name: DAOFactory Description: This class provides the methods that return data access objects which implement the DAO interfaces.
    DatabaseDeleter
    Class Name: DatabaseDeleter Description: This class contains the methods called using data access objects to Delete information from the database, and also methods which call these methods directly.
    DatabaseReader
    Class Name: DatabaseReader Description: This class contains the methods called using data access objects to Read information from the database, and also methods which call these methods directly.
    DatabaseWriter
    Class Name: DatabaseWriter Description: This class contains the methods called using data access objects to Write information to the database, and also methods which call these methods directly.
    DeleteHelper
    Class Name: DeleteHelper Description: This class contains the methods called from the DatabaseDeleter class to support the methods used there.
    ReadHelper
    Class Name: ReadHelper Description: This class contains the methods called from the DatabaseReader class to support the methods used there.
    RFIDTextReader  
    WriteHelper
    Class Name: WriteHelper Description: This class contains the methods called from the DatabaseWriter class to support the methods used there.
